      <title>泰晤士水务所有者债务违约，危机加深</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/thames-water-owner-kemble-sends-default-notice-to-creditors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰晤士水务有限公司的控股公司因未能支付利息而拖欠了约 14 亿英镑（17 亿美元）的债务，这是英国最大水务公司危机的最新升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/thames-water-owner-kemble-sends-default-notice-to-creditors</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 11:07:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于交易员推迟首次降息，国债下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/beaten-down-bond-traders-are-betting-jobs-data-means-more-losses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于数据显示美国劳动力市场活跃，几乎没有可能促使美联储降息的压力，债券交易员今年的艰难开局变得更加糟糕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/beaten-down-bond-traders-are-betting-jobs-data-means-more-losses</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 09:15:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业数据显示美国正在向前发展，股市上涨：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一份井喷的就业报告表明美国经济将继续为美国企业提供动力之后，股市本周以积极的势头结束。即使这意味着利率仍有可能上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 22:09:03 GMT</pubDate>
